FBIS4-26888 "drchi124_k_94018" FBIS-CHI-94-124 Daily Report 24 Jun 1994 NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political & Social New `Reading Activities' Paper To Be Published New `Reading Activities' Paper To Be Published OW2706122194 Beijing XINHUA Domestic Service in Chinese 2102 GMT 24 Jun 94 OW2706122194 Beijing XINHUA Domestic Service Chinese BFN [By reporter Zhang Dawei (1728 1129 3634)] [Text] Beijing, 25 Jun (XINHUA) -- ZHONGHUA DUSHU BAO [0022 5478 6236 2579 1032--CHINESE READERS NEWS] will be published in July. A national newspaper catering to reading activities, it is jointly managed by the Press and Publication Administration and GUANGMING RIBAO publishers under the cosponsorship of the latter and the Chinese Publishers' Association. To increase the newspaper's popularity, to heighten public interest in reading, and to promote the development of reading activities, the publishers and the Shenzhen Gelan Information Company have given free copies of the newspaper to 20,000 readers throghout the country.
